Package: btable
Title: Create Balance Tables Comparing Treatment and Control as Standard in Economics
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Vincent", "Thorne", , "vthorne@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6986-0816"))
Description: This package lets the users easily create balance tables as they are 
    commonly displayed in economics. Users have to specify the identifying variables, 
    the grouping (or treatment) variable, and a set of variables to check the balance of. 
    The table reports, for each treatment group and overall, the mean, standard error, 
    mean difference between groups and p-value of the mean difference. The table may be 
    save to a LaTeX file.
    Uses the excellent `data.table` and `gt` packages.
